                     <rubric>Epitaffium ad sepulcrum dantis in Rauenna urbe factum per dominum Bernardum de <sic>Canatro</sic></rubric>
                     <incipit>Iura monarchie superos flegetonta lacusque</incipit>
                    <note>This is the only manuscript to give the author's name.</note>
                     <textLang mainLang="la">Latin</textLang>
